<div class="title">Potentiating Adderall with Baking Soda</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=waldo&Exact=1">waldo</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; waldo. "Potentiating Adderall with Baking Soda: An Experience with Amphetamines (exp6430)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Feb 26, 2002. erowid.org/exp/6430</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
